  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will evaluate safety, tolerability, pharmacokinetics and pharmacodynamics of
      albinterferon alfa 2b (alb-IFN) single dose in Japanese chronic hepatitis C patients
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
